name: YabaiGang #020 - Captain Opoki
description:
"Surprise Earthling. 
Seems like you forgot that your people stole resources from Mars. Yabai..

I'd like to have them all back. My REVENGE! All of the people you've reaped selfishly. Peace? No. Look. Bright blue, huh? Yeah, photon beams to your nation. Bye."
